MetadataObject
public class RolapPrimaryDimensionOrganization
extends PrimaryDimensionOrganization

A PrimaryDimensionOrganization for a relational deployment of an MdmPrimaryDimension. To get an existing RolapPrimaryDimensionOrganization or to create a new one, use the findOrCreateRolapPrimaryDimensionOrganization method of the MdmPrimaryDimension.
